.TH projects 5
.SH NAME
projects \- persistent project root definition
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.I /etc/projects
file serves up a mappin between numeric project identifiers n' dem directories
which is tha rootz of tha quota tree.  Its format is simply:

.nf
.sp
.in +5
# comments is hash-prefixed
# ...
10:/export/cage
42:/var/log
.in -5
.fi
.PP
The
.I /etc/projects
file is optional, instead
.BR xfs_quota (8)
can be used wit the
.B \-p
argument ta specify a project root directly fo' each operation.

.SH SEE ALSO
.BR xfs_quota (8),
.BR xfsctl (3),
.BR projid (5).
